    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《积木爆射英雄》是一款快节奏Roguelite第一人称射击游戏，在游戏中，叛逆捣蛋的玩具占领了房屋，只有你能阻止它们！组装你专属的积木爆射英雄，利用古怪的武器，将敌人炸成塑料碎片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>混乱的FPS冒险</strong>中独自游玩，或与好友同乐，<strong>畅玩3人联机模式</strong>！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>使用古怪的武器</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151140/extras/8cf318ec051b4d98d0d2be878b0a9489.poster.avif?t=1772194240\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151140/extras/8cf318ec051b4d98d0d2be878b0a9489.webm?t=1772194240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151140/extras/8cf318ec051b4d98d0d2be878b0a9489.mp4?t=1772194240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >砰！！使用让任何玩具爱好者都羡慕不已的强大军火库炸飞捣蛋的玩具！<strong>自制霰弹枪？</strong>装弹完毕，锁定目标！<strong>恐龙形状的左轮手枪？</strong>靠你啦！<strong>煎锅、爆炸弓、爆能机枪</strong>…还有更多！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索巨大的房屋</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151140/extras/0508e95b63eedde5221c8403c19dca8e.poster.avif?t=1772194240\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151140/extras/0508e95b63eedde5221c8403c19dca8e.webm?t=1772194240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151140/extras/0508e95b63eedde5221c8403c19dca8e.mp4?t=1772194240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>宏伟开阔的宅邸竞技场</strong>中，选择属于你自己的路线！每一轮游戏都会带来<strong>新的布局、新的挑战和新的秘密</strong>。小心屋内的危险——当你变成玩具大小，哪怕儿童泳池都会相对变成一片汪洋大海！回到你的卧室总部，解锁升级，与袜子木偶好友聊天，并为下一次战斗做准备</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>根据你的游戏风格更换部件</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151140/extras/12cbbc2f6090429ec8f3843fe722462c.poster.avif?t=1772194240\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151140/extras/12cbbc2f6090429ec8f3843fe722462c.webm?t=1772194240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151140/extras/12cbbc2f6090429ec8f3843fe722462c.mp4?t=1772194240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个身体部位——手臂、腿部、头部和躯干——都拥有<strong>独特的技能</strong>，让你在每一轮游戏中都能自定义自己的游戏风格。将特殊技能与随机道具相结合，探索<strong>大胆的技能组合</strong>，将玩具般大小的战士变成一股不可阻挡的力量！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>直面疯狂的玩具恐怖分子</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151140/extras/45a1e0e5e33fee6032810ca61b4a05e0.poster.avif?t=1772194240\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151140/extras/45a1e0e5e33fee6032810ca61b4a05e0.webm?t=1772194240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151140/extras/45a1e0e5e33fee6032810ca61b4a05e0.mp4?t=1772194240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与狂暴的玩具哨兵、泽普骑士、鲨鱼怪、可怕的恐龙<strong>掠夺者</strong>以及众多其他致命的玩具威胁展开对决！发挥你的极限技能：闪避、射击、智胜敌人，并击败最强大的头目，夺回宅邸！</p>",
